Overview of verb pause

The verb pause has 2 senses (first 2 from tagged texts)
                                          
1. (23) hesitate, pause -- (interrupt temporarily an activity before continuing; "The speaker paused")
2. (12) pause, intermit, break -- (cease an action temporarily; "We pause for station identification"; "let's break for lunch")
